[0.000, "o", "[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32mI have successfully completed all 6 acceptance criteria for the command-line\u001b[0m \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32mTODO list application:\u001b[0m                                                       \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m### ✅ **Criterion 1: CLI Structure**\u001b[0m                                        \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Created `todo.py` with argparse-based CLI supporting add/list/complete \u001b[0m    \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32msubcommands\u001b[0m                                                                  \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Implemented proper command-line argument parsing with help text\u001b[0m            \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m### ✅ **Criterion 2: Add Command**\u001b[0m                                          \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m"]
[0.000, "o", "- Implemented task addition with auto-incrementing IDs\u001b[0m                       \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Adds ISO-format timestamps\u001b[0m                                                 \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Persists to JSON file in user's home directory (`~/.todo_list.json`)\u001b[0m       \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m### ✅ **Criterion 3: List Command**\u001b[0m                                         \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Displays all tasks with formatting\u001b[0m                                         \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Shows status (PENDING/COMPLETED) with visual symbols (○/✓)\u001b[0m                 \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Displays creation and completion timestamps\u001b[0m                                \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m### ✅ **Criterion "]
[0.000, "o", "4: Complete Command**\u001b[0m                                     \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Marks tasks as completed by ID\u001b[0m                                             \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Records completion timestamp\u001b[0m                                               \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Prevents duplicate completion\u001b[0m                                              \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m                                                                              \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m### ✅ **Criterion 5: Error Handling**\u001b[0m                                       \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m│\u001b[0m \u001b[32m- Handles missing file\u001b[0m                                                       \u001b[32m│\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[32m╰──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────╯\u001b[0m\r\n"]
